  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>Yes</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the acute effect of a preload of sucralose in presence of carbohydrate (HC)
      available on the glycemic response, postprandial C peptide and satiety in patients with type
      2 diabetes mellitus (DM2) in intensive insulin therapy (IIT).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
